{"tid":648423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺老人家特別賤格","createTime":"2018-04-30T16:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T10:15:29.000Z","uid":11779,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9813d460148570abee02079600f8605d216b91f2","tid":648423,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"唔係話所有 但一般係冇公德心心同自私自利，濫用醫療服務，明明少少病都排急症 阻住有需要嘅人，又係社工前扮慘呃縰援又鐘意屌鳩後生唔讓，食煙又會噴人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明點解啲左膠成日偏幫啲老野，老人家要受尊重前應該要先尊重其他人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c158a07af459db19e6ecea82755dc49e1b60ccfe","tid":648423,"uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"一半啦只可以咁講，有啲真係好好人遇過都會幫手<br />\n但衰嘅，試個俾啲死廢老撞完都唔道歉，我即場屌咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d85da114b667222d6f12d0c3eb6319a082264d","tid":648423,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"恃老賣老係日積月累，可能老人後生時受好多氣，到老咗&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"5768bdf430ea7d93d460fdc9762c00abe1275c4f","tid":648423,"uid":93792,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"老人唔賤 係賤人變老了"},{"pid":"515acbd181488f74ff5490a6dc76b358a1c5dbd6","tid":648423,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"一路行街，一路食煙！"},{"pid":"c28eb98a1ee237fdf89e686069b4840890810093","tid":648423,"uid":176366,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"覺啊　不過有啲老人家都幾有教養<br />\n<br />\n有次搭巴士，個頭唔舒服，無幾耐有個老人家拍我膀頭問我洗唔洗坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但賤格都